01:01:07.132 --> 01:01:19.598
But as it was moving in front of my face, I could see the sun go up and down as it moved, and everything was moving in front of my face so quickly.

01:01:19.599 --> 01:01:32.842
Sometimes the Lord would allow it to go slower on something that He felt was very important, like His crucifixion. Everything was moving very quickly.

01:01:32.843 --> 01:01:42.078
As it was moving, He was showing me it was divided by thousands of years, down to hundreds of years, down to ten years.

01:01:42.079 --> 01:01:49.947
It was all divided, and there were timelines. On every single one of them, there was a line that stated the year and what it was.

01:01:49.948 --> 01:01:55.968
Then I could see Chinese men riding on horseback. I saw people fighting with bows and arrows.

01:01:55.969 --> 01:02:05.514
I could see World War I and II; it was all being played out in front of my face. But that's whenever it got down to where we are right now.

01:02:05.515 --> 01:02:12.247
And He said, "This dispensation of grace, this right here where we are—you have a sliver of just right here, Brandon.

01:02:12.248 --> 01:02:18.479
Everything that you've ever known, everything that humanity has ever known, is coming to an end.

01:02:18.480 --> 01:02:30.558
My Son is coming. Everything."And I saw it from the beginning. Earth looked like a ball of nothingness.

01:02:30.559 --> 01:02:40.380
As He spoke it into existence, it was without form and void, and darkness was on the face of the deep.

01:02:40.381 --> 01:02:47.376
I could see it. People want to argue about it being a flat earth. It was not a flat earth; it's a ball.

01:02:47.377 --> 01:02:53.908
People go, "Well, Brandon, that doesn't line up."I'm telling you, it was a ball.

01:02:53.909 --> 01:02:59.583
It looked like a lump of clay. It was darkness; there was nothing.

01:02:59.584 --> 01:03:06.674
It was nothingness. As He spoke it, it all started to come about.

01:03:06.675 --> 01:03:16.798
I saw it. Then I saw Adam in the garden. He had a perfect beard; everything was perfect.

01:03:16.799 --> 01:03:25.759
I tried to tell people what Eve looked like. Eve had beautiful eyes.

01:03:25.760 --> 01:03:34.719
They were the most beautiful color of eyes; I've never seen eyes like them since.

01:03:34.720 --> 01:03:44.879
She was olive-skinned. She wasn't white, and she was not African-American dark.

01:03:44.880 --> 01:03:54.710
She was dark; she was like tan—very tan, darker than American Indian skin.

01:03:54.711 --> 01:04:04.283
Not that it matters, but people want to know. She looked oliveish.

01:04:04.284 --> 01:04:16.900
People ask, "What does that look like?"No, very dark like tan skin, but her hair was blacker than Diana's hair.

01:04:16.901 --> 01:04:24.100
Her eyes were the most beautiful color I've ever seen. In fact, I've tried to explain them to Diana.

01:04:24.101 --> 01:04:27.629
We've tried to find people's eyes that look like Eve's eyes.

01:04:27.630 --> 01:04:46.569
I said, "If I ever find them, Diana, I'll show you."They looked almost a greenish color with a mixture of brown and a little blue in them.

01:04:46.570 --> 01:04:59.101
Explain that—it was beautiful, the eye. I didn't see Adam's eyes, but Eve was sitting down with her hair around her.

01:04:59.102 --> 01:05:14.529
I saw her sitting on a little rock with ferns growing around her, and she was doing something, but it happened quickly.

01:05:14.530 --> 01:05:28.239
I was thinking, "What in the world?"Everything in the garden at that moment was glorious.

01:05:28.240 --> 01:05:37.519
It was beautiful going back and being able to see that again.

01:05:37.520 --> 01:05:44.331
Birds were the size of cars; they were truly massive. It was prehistoric.

01:05:44.332 --> 01:05:52.585
It was beautiful. Things weren't like now. Things were bigger: the trees were bigger, the plants were bigger.

01:05:52.586 --> 01:06:00.091
So, is that enough? I don't know if I answered that right. But I could see the pyramids; I could see everything being constructed.

01:06:00.092 --> 01:06:10.129
I think people think there are conspiracies happening, which is why they are asking about conspiracies—how it was built.

01:06:10.130 --> 01:06:13.598
I saw men building them. I didn't see aliens building the pyramids.

01:06:13.599 --> 01:06:20.588
They were men building the pyramids, and they had wooden things. They were dragging things around.

01:06:20.589 --> 01:06:27.802
People ask, "How'd that happen?"There were literally hundreds, if not thousands, of men moving these things around.

01:06:27.803 --> 01:06:34.363
I could see all these ramps and all this stuff being moved around.

01:06:34.364 --> 01:06:39.602
People say, "Well, how'd they lift a big stone like that?"They did. But there were bigger men.

01:06:39.603 --> 01:06:49.809
Now, if those were giants, I don't know, but it was happening quickly and panning out before my face.

01:06:49.810 --> 01:06:55.542
It was happening so fast that it was moving like this, and I was trying to glimpse it.

01:06:55.543 --> 01:07:09.778
I was looking at the Chinese Empire and all the things going on with the Great Wall of China; it was all being constructed right in front of my face.

01:07:09.779 --> 01:07:22.639
The Lord was just showing me things about time. And the city of Atlantis was out by Africa.

01:07:22.640 --> 01:07:32.796
It was an actual city. I saw it being swallowed up by fire and water. As it was playing out for me, I knew what it was.

01:07:32.797 --> 01:07:40.325
The Lord said to me, "This is the lost city of Atlantis."It was a mass—not just a little town.

01:07:40.326 --> 01:07:49.279
We're talking a massive thing, almost like an island, and it was destroyed.

01:07:49.280 --> 01:07:52.472
I could see the storm. I could see lightning. I could see things.

01:07:52.473 --> 01:07:58.299
There was something that happened. Brandon, that's way out there.

01:07:58.300 --> 01:08:07.552
A lot of things I don't share, because people—that's why I say if I can't usually back it up in scripture or whatever, I don't talk about a lot of things.

01:08:07.553 --> 01:08:14.162
But tonight I thought, well, I didn't have a lot. But I'll tell you some of the things I've seen and it's kind of interesting.

01:08:14.163 --> 01:08:20.866
I just keep a lot of things to myself. I just go, 'Well, you know, it's way out there.

01:08:20.867 --> 01:08:25.362
Are people going to believe it?'Well, there were dinosaurs, folks, and they were walking around Adam.

01:08:25.363 --> 01:08:35.459
It was a massive looking long-neck dinosaur, and he was talking to it, and it understood him as it was eating the trees.

01:08:35.460 --> 01:08:41.395
And Adam was talking to this thing. I don't know how it was like—did he speak dinosaur? I have no idea.

01:08:41.396 --> 01:08:46.497
But the dinosaur, like we talk to dogs and they listen to us, animals were listening to him.

01:08:46.498 --> 01:08:59.673
And that's why I was like, 'Look at that.'That big old long-neck dinosaur looks like one of those brachiosauruses that you know, like those long-neck dinosaurs on Jurassic Park.

01:08:59.675 --> 01:09:10.404
It was huge. It looked like a thunder lizard, a massive lizard, but I don't know.

01:09:10.405 --> 01:09:16.316
Father, we just thank you, Lord, for the body. Thank you, Lord, for all that you've done for us.

01:09:16.317 --> 01:09:24.004
