01:11:08.830 --> 01:11:17.359
That is very interesting. When I was holding the body, thank you Lord.

01:11:17.360 --> 01:11:22.636
Hallelujah. Diana, you believe for anything? I bless you in Jesus'name.

01:11:22.637 --> 01:11:28.656
Father, I thank you Lord for my wife healed and whole and well and filled with the power of God in Jesus'name.

01:11:28.657 --> 01:11:33.168
I feel if it's there, it's there for a reason. He doesn't just do that.

01:11:33.169 --> 01:11:40.095
Thank you Lord for the blood in Jesus'name. I'm actually feeling like I'm getting drunk in the Holy Ghost.

01:11:40.096 --> 01:12:48.079
That is amazing. Hallelujah. Wow. Hallelujah. Hallelujah.

01:12:48.080 --> 01:13:05.678
Wow. My tongue got it. Oh my goodness, Lord. Well, thank you, being filled with the Holy Ghost.

01:13:05.679 --> 01:13:14.310
Thank you, Lord, for the blood. Thank you, Father, that we make much of the blood and the blood makes much of us.

