We put angels all around and about us. Father, I thank you, Lord.

01:14:11.058 --> 01:14:14.980
Though we make much of the blood, we take the blood right now, Father.

01:14:14.981 --> 01:14:29.353
We thank you, Lord, that you forgive us of our sins in the name of Jesus.

01:14:29.354 --> 01:15:09.599
Amen and amen. You want a drink, baby? Thank you. Thank you, Lord.

