01:15:36.239 --> 01:15:52.158
Bread of heaven, feed me till I want no more. Fill my cup, fill it up and make me whole.

01:15:52.159 --> 01:16:10.319
Fill our cup, Lord. I lift it up, Lord. Come and quench this thirsting of my soul.

01:16:10.320 --> 01:16:27.839
Bread of heaven, feed me till I want no more. Fill my cup. Fill it up and make me whole.

01:16:27.840 --> 01:17:01.759
Thank you, Lord. Fill our cup, Lord. I lift it up, Lord. Come and quench this thirsting of our soul.

01:17:01.760 --> 01:17:20.559
Bread of heaven, feed me till I want no more. Fill our cup. Fill it up and make me whole.

