I wish in the natural I could draw the pictures of what I saw, even about the pyramids and the things that I saw, the way the people looked as they were building things.

01:17:40.239 --> 01:17:54.479
The things that I have inside of me are such treasures. I could share them with everyone.

01:17:54.480 --> 01:18:10.718
How beautiful life is for all of us and we don't know it. Life is but a vapor and it moves so quickly.

01:18:10.719 --> 01:18:20.157
It's just a blink. What do we do with the blink we have? What do we do with the blink God's given us?

01:18:20.158 --> 01:18:29.919
It goes so quickly. What do we do with the relationship that he wants to have with every one of us?

01:18:29.920 --> 01:18:50.799
Life is a blink. Blink twice and it's over. Jesus, let us do something great in that blink.

01:18:50.800 --> 01:19:20.639
Oh Father, I thank you Lord. Every one of us has something that God's called us to do.

01:19:20.640 --> 01:19:32.319
We do it with all our heart. Oh Lord, I thank you for your relationship.

01:19:32.320 --> 01:20:12.639
Oh Lord, you're beautiful. Your face is all I seek. And when your eyes are on this child, your grace abounds to me.

01:20:12.640 --> 01:20:38.959
Oh Lord, you're beautiful. Your face is all I see. Thank you, Father.

01:20:38.960 --> 01:20:47.279
There's so many of you that just need refreshed. He said he'll bring the refreshing.

01:20:47.280 --> 01:20:54.423
He'll bring the rain. He'll bring the rain on you. He'll bring the rain.

01:20:54.424 --> 01:21:06.238
It's like I had last night. I sat there and said, 'Lord, bring the rain. Jesus, I am thirsty.

01:21:06.239 --> 01:21:27.678
I've poured out, Lord, and I need a fresh touch.'All you need is a drink. There's so many people here tonight that just need a drink.

