01:21:44.248 --> 01:21:54.638
Jesus wants to become real to you. The Holy Spirit wants to become real to you.

01:21:54.639 --> 01:22:13.839
He's not a dove. He's not a feeling. He is a person. And he is more real to me than Diana is.

01:22:13.840 --> 01:22:19.330
I'm telling you, when he appeared and I was able to see him for the glimpse that I had, he's green.

01:22:19.331 --> 01:22:28.808
He's beautiful. He's alive. That probably just wrecked some people's world.

01:22:28.809 --> 01:22:43.198
But as I saw it, he's an all-consuming fire, but he's green. It's like blue fire.

01:22:43.199 --> 01:22:50.959
An all-consuming fire that's blue but just has a green tint to it.

01:22:50.960 --> 01:23:07.354
The Holy Spirit has a form and he's barrel-chested. He's huge.

01:23:07.355 --> 01:23:17.167
I'm talking like a thick barrel-chested man. The Holy Spirit is not skinny.

01:23:17.168 --> 01:23:35.919
He's barrel-chested. He looks like he has a 50-gallon wood barrel. That's how thick his chest is.

01:23:35.920 --> 01:23:47.839
I was allowed to see these glimpses when he came and talked to me one day and I said, 'Oh, it's nothing what I thought.

01:23:47.840 --> 01:24:24.399
He's massive.'But he wants to become more so real to you. Oh Jesus.

01:24:24.400 --> 01:24:54.471
People want to know, 'Brandon, how do you have these experiences?'But every single one of them is so dear to me. I'll never forget any of them.

01:24:54.472 --> 01:25:06.079
It's like whenever you have something and you burn it on a piece of leather, it's ingrained there forever like cowhide.

01:25:06.080 --> 01:25:14.879
You brand it. Those experiences are branded in my mind. They're branded in me.

01:25:14.880 --> 01:25:25.011
They're always there. I can recall them. My mom said, "Brandon, you always have a memory like an elephant.

01:25:25.012 --> 01:25:33.903
You don't forget nothing."I know, but they truly are there, every single one of them, going to tribulation.

01:25:33.904 --> 01:25:49.278
I can recall them. They really happened. Every instance is so beautiful, and all the experiences that I've had with the Father.

01:25:49.279 --> 01:25:54.685
I can bring it back—from every angel encounter I've had to the demonic—I don't forget it.

01:25:54.686 --> 01:26:04.853
I remember it, and the Lord shows it to me and I recall it as much as my wedding day.

01:26:04.854 --> 01:26:09.265
You never forget it. You never forget the day you got born again.

01:26:09.266 --> 01:26:20.718
You never forget the day your first child was born or your children were born. You don't forget it.

01:26:20.719 --> 01:26:31.279
When I've seen glimpses of heaven, I'm telling you all, you don't want to miss it.

01:26:31.280 --> 01:26:46.632
He's prepared a place for you that's so beautiful, and he wants you to go so bad. And to be absent from the body is to be present with the Lord.

01:26:46.633 --> 01:27:06.836
You know, whenever you almost died giving birth to Paisley, Diana said when she was stepping over and the doctor almost lost her after her C-section, her blood pressure dropped so bad.

01:27:06.837 --> 01:27:25.548
She said, "You tell them what you felt."Whenever it was, it was as easy as—it was easier than anything I've ever experienced in my life.

01:27:25.549 --> 01:27:35.919
It was just like breathing and I felt such a peace, just more peace than I've ever had in my whole life.

01:27:35.920 --> 01:27:45.039
And it was like breathing, like I was there. It would have been easier to go than it would have been to stay.

01:27:45.040 --> 01:28:13.468
And I really, really wanted to go because this peace was indescribable, peace on another level that a human can't understand, because the Holy Spirit brings so much peace to us here in this body, in our earthly vessels.

01:28:13.469 --> 01:28:41.999
But whenever I was in that moment, I can't describe it. I have no vocabulary to describe it, but it was beautiful and it felt like the way we're supposed to be, like the way we're supposed to feel.

01:28:42.000 --> 01:28:51.198
That peace just makes you feel alive, like this is life. It didn't feel like dying; it felt like living.

01:28:51.199 --> 01:29:00.879
I don't know how else to describe it. It was beautiful. I'll never forget it.

01:29:00.880 --> 01:29:06.578
I have no vocabulary; that's the closest thing I can get to describing it.

01:29:06.579 --> 01:29:13.467
I remember seeing your eyes and I told her, "You're going to lose her. She's going."And I could see it. I could feel it.

01:29:13.468 --> 01:29:18.879
And I grabbed a hold of your foot and I was praying, "No, you ain't dying on me.

01:29:18.880 --> 01:29:30.158
You ain't dying on me."They rushed in there and she coded, and they brought all their nurses in there to help her.

01:29:30.159 --> 01:29:40.959
I remember thinking, "She's slipping over right now. She's leaving me,"and they brought her back.

01:29:40.960 --> 01:30:01.830
You know, that in-between, that place where you're about ready to go home—in that instance where Diana was in birth like that and she lost so much blood, it was really scary in the natural for me, but I could see the peace on her face.

01:30:01.831 --> 01:30:10.346
And she said, "Pray for me."And all of a sudden, that was the last thing she said for a second, and she went poof and her eyes got dark.

01:30:10.347 --> 01:30:22.412
I went, "What's going on? Is she truly about to die?"But they brought her back, all to the glory of God.

01:30:22.413 --> 01:30:36.439
Thank you, Jesus. I just try to bring the Lord in these things.

01:30:36.440 --> 01:30:41.759
When he visits and he's talking, I feel his presence so strong right now.

01:30:41.760 --> 01:30:52.006
I want you to realize that he wants a relationship more with you than what you want one with him.

01:30:52.007 --> 01:30:58.155
It's more real, y'all, than what your grandma's preacher told you or whatever.

01:30:58.156 --> 01:31:04.819
Jesus is real and the Holy Spirit is real, and they want a relationship with you.

01:31:04.820 --> 01:31:12.762
