01:32:20.782 --> 01:32:28.400
I've dumped out all week and I just need you to help me."I said, "Are you mad at me?

01:32:28.401 --> 01:32:34.399
Is our relationship cooled off out of insecurity?"I said, "Lord, are we cool?

01:32:34.400 --> 01:32:37.919
Are we alright?"He said, "Brandon, you're tired. I'm not mad at you.

01:32:37.920 --> 01:32:58.718
Why would I be mad at you? You've helped me, Brandon. I want to help you."But I don't want to lose myself in all this.

01:32:58.719 --> 01:33:14.830
You can gain the whole world and lose your soul. I don't want to lose my relationship with you because of the people pulling all the time.

01:33:14.831 --> 01:33:24.638
But I understood why the disciples took their time and they gave it away, but at the same time it's so desperate because there's so many people with so many needs.

01:33:24.639 --> 01:33:30.541
There's so many people that are going to hell. There's so many people that just don't know.

01:33:30.542 --> 01:33:43.832
